{
  "stem": "11723.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And finally, they got the statue down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I said to my sister, let's get out of here because we're going to get trampled.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And they put out a rope around the-- the statute.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And they attached it to some sort of vehicle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And they paraded it through the entire city, and people spit on it and, uh, did other things on it, too, that I'm not going to mention.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And people chipped away at it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Everybody wanted a souvenir.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And, uh, then we went home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And that night, we heard shots.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "My mother and I went outside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And we heard shots.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And I knew it wasn't going to be a bloodless revolution.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the next morning-- and my father, of course, was out of town, because that was his job.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know where he was and when he's going to get home and what is going to happen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the first thing, I'm going to go get bread, right?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The first thing in the morning, like 6 or 7 o'clock, I run down, and I stand in line for bread.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I hear all-- all of this shooting, all over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also, I saw that some of the, uh, cobblestones were thrown up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Russians were in there with their tanks already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, uh, they tore up the street where I lived in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They came through with this huge tanks and-- on those narrow streets and tore up the pavement and everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were sitting ducks in those tanks, because the kids were throwing Molotov cocktails at them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, uh, more often than not, they were successful-- I mean, the kids.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And those people just fried in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
